{\"sentence\": \"And he did it and he came home.\\\"\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 3000, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During an interview withGlamoura month later, Mendes explained her parenting agreement with Gosling, noting that it wasn't a \\\"non-verbal\\\" one that led her to work from home.\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather, Gosling and Mendes had many deep conversations about balancing both their professional and family lives, she said.\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me\\u2026 recently in an interview I said it was almost like non-verbal agreement Ryan and I had [to step back from acting].\", \"from\": 3300, \"to\": 3423, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3381, \"end\": 3385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"score\": 0.9999360460834887, \"rank\": 4.425006217230137e-05, \"text\": \"Ryan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nolan_Ryan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That got\\u2026 not twisted, but taken out of context because I meant it was almost a no-brainer.\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3515, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But there was actually obviously a lot of thought and conversation - especially on my end - of what I wanted to do with my life,\\\" theHitchstar explained.\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3669, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3901, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3722, \"end\": 3733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.8038641495138575e-15, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \